Connections Recap:
Ultrasonic Sensor (HC-SR04):

TRIG Pin → Pin 9 (Arduino)
ECHO Pin → Pin 10 (Arduino)
VCC → 5V on Arduino
GND → GND on Arduino
Soil Moisture Sensor:

Analog Output Pin → Pin A0 (Arduino)
VCC → 5V on Arduino
GND → GND on Arduino
Relay Module:

IN Pin → Pin 7 (Arduino)
NO Pin → Positive terminal of the pump
COM Pin → 12V positive rail for pump power
VCC → 5V on Arduino
GND → GND on Arduino
GSM Module:

TX Pin → Pin 2 (Arduino)
RX Pin → Pin 3 (Arduino)
VCC → 5V (or 4.2V if using an external 5V supply)
GND → GND on Arduino
I2C LCD:

SDA Pin → A4 (Arduino Uno)
SCL Pin → A5 (Arduino Uno)
VCC → 5V on Arduino
GND → GND on Arduino
